    <forecast>
        <area aac="SA_FA001" description="South Australia" type="region">
            <forecast-period start-time-local="2026-06-19T15:55:57+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-19T15:55:57+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-19T06:25:57Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-19T06:25:57Z">
                <text type="warning_summary_footer">For latest warnings go to www.bom.gov.au, subscribe to RSS feeds, call 1300 659 210* or listen for warnings on relevant TV and radio broadcasts.</text>
                <text type="synoptic_situation">A low pressure system over Bass Strait will move eastwards and weaken overnight. An associated cold front will move slowly across the southeast of SA and will clear to the east during Saturday morning. A high pressure system will become established over the Bight during Saturday then will move only slowly eastwards during Sunday and Monday. A low pressure trough will move across southern coastal districts on Tuesday then another high will move across waters to the south.</text>
                <text type="product_footer">* Calls to 1300 numbers cost around 27.5c incl. GST, higher from mobiles or public phones.</text>
            </forecast-period>
        </area>
        <area aac="SA_PW014" description="North East Pastoral" type="public-district" parent-aac="SA_FA001">
            <forecast-period index="0" start-time-local="2026-06-19T15:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-20T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-19T05:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-19T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers south of Leigh Creek, near zero chance elsewhere. Winds westerly 20 to 30 km/h decreasing to 15 to 20 km/h in the evening.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-06-20T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-21T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-19T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-20T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers south of Leigh Creek, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Near zero chance of rain elsewhere. Winds west to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending south to southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning then decreasing to 15 to 20 km/h in the late afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 6 and 9 with daytime temperatures reaching between 14 and 18.</text>
                <text type="uv_alert">##</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-06-21T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-22T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-20T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-21T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog south of Leigh Creek. Slight chance of a shower about the Gammon Ranges, near zero chance elsewhere. The chance of morning frost south of Yunta. Winds southerly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light in the late afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 4 and 7 with daytime temperatures reaching between 14 and 18.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-06-22T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-23T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-21T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-22T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog south of Yunta. Winds south to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending east to southeasterly during the morning then tending south to southeasterly during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 3 and 7 with daytime temperatures reaching between 14 and 19.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="4" start-time-local="2026-06-23T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-24T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-22T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-23T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. The chance of morning fog south of Leigh Creek. The chance of morning frost south of Leigh Creek. Winds southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to between 3 and 7 with daytime temperatures reaching between 15 and 18.</text>
            </forecast-period>
        </area>
